  mark: 'Smithsonian Institution Oral and Visual Histories, Oral History Interview with Lawrence Ellison (19951024).',
  quote: 'When I started Oracle, what I wanted to do was to create an environment where I would enjoy working. That was my primary goal. Sure, I wanted to make a living. I certainly never expected to become rich, certainly not this rich. I mean, rich does not even describe this. This is surreal.'
